                  4
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Temporary Furnished Housing</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  Furnished temporary apartments in Lausanne (CHF 1,800-3,500/month) while searching for permanent housing. Options near universities, lakefront, or city center. Many researchers and corporate expats use temporary housing during first 1-3 months. Students often need temporary accommodation for first semester while finding permanent apartments to share. Agencies coordinate temporary and permanent housing timing, ensuring smooth transition. Advance booking essential for August-September academic year start. Flexible short-term contracts available.
